This course was EXCEPTIONAL! It had everything in it that I was "missing" from other Fiverr courses on SEO. I LOVED how this course was so well written. It covered everything I wanted to know and brush up on and even included SEO terminology breakdown (which is both a helpful reminder to experts and a helpful guide to beginners). I believe that SEO experts and SEO beginners can both walk away from this course feeling informed, competent, and empowered. Whether you are a blogger, site owner, SEO specialist, or content writer, if you can only afford "one" course this is the course. If you are looking to up your SEO game or SEO credibility here on Fiverr, THIS is the course. Ironically, this course was shorter than many of the other courses. I can tell their course writer knew exactly what they were doing, and since time is so valuable, I really appreciated that. This course was condensed but it packed a comprehensive and very thorough punch. I didn't feel like anything was missing, and I highly recommend it for anyone looking to learn more about SEO.

Overall, I would highly recommend this course to anyone who wants to improve their technical SEO skills and knowledge. I feel much more confident in my ability to conduct a thorough technical SEO audit after completing this course.
